{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow multiple successions of social housing tenancies",
        "additional_details": "There are many people who can\u2019t afford their own home & some have commitments i.e live at home to look after a loved one. If the rule was changed it would prevent anxiety & fear of not having somewhere to live.",
        "background": "The law currently states a housing association or council tenancy can only be passed on once. I am asking for the rules on tenancies to be changed to allow multiple successions of the same tenancy.",
